# Force LF line endings in the Git index for all text files.
# Working-tree copies on Windows will be checked out as LF too (matching
# the Prettier "endOfLine": "lf" setting), so there are zero conversion
# surprises when switching between Windows and WSL.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly mark known binary formats so Git never tries to diff/merge them.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
